{"tid":779402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際突發】意大利熱那亞行車天橋倒冧 成段橋身消失咗","createTime":"2018-08-14T11:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T13:18:36.000Z","uid":53484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"35a739dfbc6e03d1a8bf815b4cb70eccb2ed4f43","tid":779402,"uid":53484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"外電報道，意大利北部港口城市熱那亞附近的一條行車天橋倒冧，從網上流傳的圖片可見，當地一條行車天橋的一大段「消失」了，意大利傳媒估計，倒冧的橋身約有200米長。肇事天橋名為「莫蘭迪大橋」（Morandi Bridge），建於1968年，是當地A10公路的一部份。意大利有通訊社指，事件造成了「數十人死亡」。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方及消防部門指，暫未能確定死傷人數，但估計事發時至少有數部車輛在橋面行駛，救援人員已到場進行搜救。意大利運輸部長稱，相信事件是一宗重大事故。<br />\n<br />\n身處現場的記者納迪沃（Franco Nativo）稱，至少有8至9部車從橋上跌落路面，他形容「這是末日景象」。警方指，天橋倒冧時現場天氣惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180814/58563150\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F58563150&d=DrYW53ZiRSe9wNmx%2B8wU6kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1ed978b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F58563150&h=282926f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180814/58563150</a>"},{"pid":"6a84c0d9783a80f1d18548229e0ed7e47ba8714d","tid":779402,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"希望港豬澳大橋都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b893e90558f0dc1d777d45788f856a6d9ed075d8","tid":779402,"uid":12404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:20:24.000Z","msg":"歐洲支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f975635c9a7074a036ba81c422aa353d2448d2b2","tid":779402,"uid":18167,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stratfordmartialmusic.files.wordpress.